keyMappings:
map <tab> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map <c-t> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map <c-d> scrollFullPageDown
map <c-u> scrollFullPageUp
map h previousTab
map l nextTab
map d removeTab
map u restoreTab
map H moveTabLeft
map L moveTabRight
map J goBack
map K goForward
map y copyCurrentUrl
map T Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab

unmap v
map vf createTab https://mangadex.cc/follows
map vy createTab https://www.youtube.com/feed/subscriptions
map vv createTab https://portal.victorops.com/client/status-im
map va createTab http://arael.magi.vpn/
map vm createTab http://melchior.magi.vpn/
map vg createTab https://gh.status.im/
